<p>I have the following xml format</p>  <pre><code>&lt;A&gt;  &lt;a&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;b&gt;2&lt;/b&gt;  &lt;c&gt;3&lt;/c&gt;  ........  ........ &lt;/A&gt; </code></pre>  <p>I want to format it as </p>  <pre><code> &lt;A a="1" b="2"&gt;  &lt;c&gt;3&lt;/c&gt;   ......... &lt;/A&gt; </code></pre>  <p>note: I want only first few say 2 children to convert as parent's attributes ,not all. </p>  <p>The xsl which know for converting all attributes is </p>  <pre><code>  &lt;xsl:template match="A"&gt;   &lt;A&gt;       &lt;xsl:for-each select="*"&gt;        &lt;xsl:attribute name="{name()}"&gt;            &lt;xsl:value-of select="text()"/&gt;         &lt;/xsl:attribute&gt;       &lt;/xsl:for-each&gt;    &lt;A&gt;    &lt;/xsl:template&gt; </code></pre>